<br/> <h1>Work Prayer</h1>
<br/>  <a href="Index">Index</a> 
<br/> 
<br/> Let me see my work through the eyes of Jesus.
<br/> 
<br/> I want my work life to be an act of worship.
<br/> 
<br/> Help me to love people the way that you do.
<br/> 
<br/> Teach me to be a representative of your kingdom.
<br/> 
<br/> Make me an example that others will emulate.
<br/> 
<br/> Remind me when it is time to lay down my goals in deferrence to others.
<br/> 
<br/> Show me the serving opportunities that you have given me.
<br/> 
<br/> Let me always extend mercy and forgiveness.
<br/> 
<br/> Surpress criticism and judgmental attitudes.
<br/> 
<br/> Give me humility, help me to admit when I am wrong.
<br/> 
<br/> Show me the courage to make changes where needed.
<br/> 
<br/> Allow me to be at peace by fully trusting you.
<br/> 
